00:04:04.790 --> 00:04:11.790
You might be wondering how it all works, well
basicaly this is the CPU microcontroller,

00:04:12.420 --> 00:04:18.840
a PICAXE 28X2, it's prorammed through here,
it is normally programmed with a USB-headphones

00:04:18.840 --> 00:04:25.840
cable but you can see here that it has a headphone
extension cable that allows you to program

00:04:27.479 --> 00:04:34.479
it from outside the case the keyboard monitor
works the same way and communicates with the

00:04:37.340 --> 00:04:44.340
