that allows multiple devices on the same two

00:04:47.030 --> 00:04:53.780
wires to communicate with each other and notice
multiple devices, so I also used this SD card

00:04:53.780 --> 00:05:00.780
reader which als uses i2c to communicate with
the CPU and it uses a single wire with the

00:05:01.889 --> 00:05:08.889
serial (UART) protocol to communicate through
this way and then to the display here.

